    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Hyouton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 2 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 15 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 3 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 15</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, E, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You fire a dart of ice and make a ranged attack roll at your highest attack bonus. If it hits, the ice dart deals 1d4+1 cold damage.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to create one additional dart, which can be fired at the same or a different enemy. Each dart requires an attack roll to hit. (Maximum 1 dart per 2 levels total).</p>\n\n",
